{"tid":1065521,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【心理學】研究發現: 逄迎及揚惡有助提高面試成功機會","createTime":"2019-03-17T10:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T13:57:56.000Z","uid":78029,"like":46,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b2d08f4d0a0f56d10edd67e9fe792cbdac8f1879","tid":1065521,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T10:22:05.000Z","msg":"大家好，小弟希望成為香港知識型Youtuber ，所以開咗一個Youtube Channel，希望我同大家可以一齊學吓唔同知識<br />\n希望大家比多D意見我改善, 因為我仲摸索緊個模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今次反傳統智慧 用4分鐘教你2個提高你面試成功率的小技巧 </span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-1fRVDvsRm0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-1fRVDvsRm0&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2FxD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=3f3863fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-1fRVDvsRm0</a>"},{"pid":"9daefa92b52c9f412b806b3cc01f32c4d51c40b9","tid":1065521,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T10:22:46.000Z","msg":"補充: <br />\n1.本集取材自《Timing of self-disclosure and its effects on personal attraction.》, 《The Effect of Applicant Influence Tactics on Recruiter Perceptions of Fit and Hiring Recommendations: A Field Study》, 《Applicant Impression Management: Dispositional<br />\nInfluences and Consequences for Recruiter Perceptions of Fit and Similarity》,《Insincere Flattery Actually Works: A Dual Attitudes Perspective》,《59 SECONDS Think A Little, Change A Lot》"},{"pid":"2ed4ab6dc281172faee384adb61c09be10defef0","tid":1065521,"uid":78029,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T10:24:58.000Z","msg":"2. 至於洗唔洗揚善, 強調HARDSELL自己強項<br />\n有研究話有幫助, 但有研究話無<br />\n取決於IN你個人係邊個, 識唔識你專業(即係外行人定內行人)<br />\n如果外行人, HARDSELL自己識幾多相關專業野其實未必有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2384d7059a1ad7496bd0e6057dc1657b555eb6ca","tid":1065521,"uid":78029,"like":0,"d